should be torn down.

06:32.417 --> 06:34.134
(sighs) God, there's a lot
wrong with this,

06:34.228 --> 06:35.301
but you can't tear this down.

06:35.454 --> 06:36.786
Pat's an icon.

06:36.888 --> 06:38.713
That statue belongs
right here in the park,

06:38.732 --> 06:41.124
next to the statue
of Quahog's greatest missionary,

06:41.226 --> 06:42.550
Father Touchboys.

06:42.611 --> 06:44.719
