a year ago.

06:44.780 --> 06:46.696
For what?!

06:53.305 --> 06:54.988
Good afternoon, I'm Tom Tucker.

06:55.082 --> 06:58.308
Our top story: the revelations
about local hero Pawtucket Pat

06:58.368 --> 07:00.234
