over whether his statue

07:02.147 --> 07:03.663
should remain in the park.

07:03.757 --> 07:06.758
Even the pigeons who poop on it
are in a moral quandary.

07:06.927 --> 07:10.411
So, what do you two think of
the statue being on public land?

07:10.472 --> 07:13.581
-Coo.
-Not coo.

