PETER:
My friend is the mailman.

07:15.218 --> 07:17.510
I'm gonna give him
a heart attack.

07:17.663 --> 07:20.346
Good job, Brian. Your work
has actually made an impact.

07:20.441 --> 07:22.107
Thanks, Stewie.
I think everybody's

07:22.300 --> 07:23.683
gonna be happy about this.

07:23.819 --> 07:25.351
Where do you get off?!

07:25.504 --> 07:28.354
In my bedroom, mostly.
Sometimes the bathroom.

07:28.490 --> 07:30.690
Or wherever I see
a lady seal an envelope.

07:30.784 --> 07:34.286
Good, good. I am glad
we can talk frankly about sex.

07:34.455 --> 07:36.362
And Brian,
how dare you try to take down

07:36.457 --> 07:38.290
the statue of Pawtucket Pat?

07:38.441 --> 07:39.365
Oh, my God.
You don't actually support

07:39.518 --> 07:40.850
