and yelled at me for two months?

08:11.775 --> 08:14.475
Peter, we've been over this.
That was the Heaven's Gate cult.

08:14.495 --> 08:16.219
Oh, right, that-that thing
with the shoes.

08:16.279 --> 08:17.979
Yeah, o-once I got the shoes,
